document.title: Bank of Thailand Warns More Account Freezes Are Incoming

document.title: Dubai Royal-Backed Fund MGX Buys 15% of TikTok U.S. Business in Major Stake Deal: Report
document.source: CoinDesk: Bitcoin, Ethereum, Crypto News and Price Data

document.title: Eric Trump Believes Bitcoin Will Reach $1 Million; Prediction Markets Say Otherwise

body.raw: Eric Trump, son of President Donald Trump, said he believes bitcoin will surpass $1 million and is extremely bullish on the cryptocurrency’s future. Prediction markets put the probability of that happening in 2025 at under 1%. Eric Trump Believes Bitcoin Will Reach Well Over $1M

document.title: NYDIG Calls for Bitcoin Treasury Companies to Drop 'Misleading' mNAV Metric
document.source: CoinDesk: Bitcoin, Ethereum, Crypto News and Price Data

document.title: Tennessee Couple Hit With $6.8 Million Penalty for 'Blessings of God Thru Crypto' Fraud

body.raw: James Wynn's new trade comes just days after being liquidated on the same token, as he believes ASTER's airdrop will be one of the biggest in crypto history.

document.title: Trump-linked WLFI burns $1.43M worth of tokens after $1M buyback
